original_title: Slotsarkitekt Thorvald Jørgensen Paa Christianborg Slots Stilladser
overview: View over the castle island of Holmen's Church and the Stock Exchange from the top of Christiansborg, where architect Thorvald Jørgensen is seen at Christiansborg slotting scaffolding, and with builders in the courtyard. The architect is also seen with stonemasons in the yard.
title: Slotsarkitekt Thorvald Jørgensen Paa Christianborg Slots Stilladser
